text: El Sherbini, El Sherbiny or El Sherbeny () is an Egyptian surname, named after the Egyptian city of Sherbin. Notable people with this surname include: * Gamal El-Sherbini, Egyptian athlete * Mimi El-Sherbini, Egyptian former footballer * Mohamed ElSherbini, Egyptian squash player * Nour El Sherbini, Egyptian squash player Category:Dakahlia Governorate Category:Egyptian families
title: El Sherbini
